        article.c-screen.u-clearfix.c-screen--about
            header
                h1 Print the Love
                p Love Polaroids is about more than just giving away a photograph. It is about hope, love, and encouragement. It is about uplifting others, helping them see the beauty in themselves regardless of their circumstance.

            section.c-left
                h3 The Impact
                p The impact of Love Polaroids is felt by across people groups, ages, races, cultures and languages. To be able to print on the spot within seconds with Polaroid products, it opens up the doors to serve those who normally wouldn’t be able to receive such a gift. In order to maximize impact, Love Polaroids hosts expeditions for those who want to particpate in the cause first hand.
                p “I wish I could bottle up the joy that Love Polaroids gives to everyone who received or gave a photo for you to feel it too. It is like joy exploding! It stays with you forever and I wish everyone on earth could feel it.” - Ceallaigh Anderson

            section.c-right
                h3 The Vision
                p It is Love Polaroids vision to see every person on earth feel loved, valued, and celebrated even amidst life’s most difficult trials. That all would have access to photographs of family, friends, and life’s most cherished memories and milestones.

            section.c-right
                h3 The Mission
                p To celebrate the value and dignity of individuals in under-resourced communities through the gift of a Love Polaroid.

            aside.u-clearfix
                section.c-left
                    div.c-img--circle
                        img(src='img/about_children.jpg')
                    h5 Children
                        span Served
                    p Children in many under-resourced communities are marginalized and often not celebrated for who they are. We want to change that! Self-worth is important for emotional and social development. Very few children get school photos taken or have any record of their childhood. As well, if a child were to be lost or taken, there would be a photograph to help find him or her.
                section.c-right
                    div.c-img--circle
                        img(src='img/about_hospitalized.jpg')
                    h5 Hospitalized
                        span Encouraged
                    p New mothers in maternity wards around the globe rarely have access to photographs of their newborns and this lifechanging event. Others who are losing a loved one, cherish the last moments they have together. Even those in the hospital for more minor issues feel the love of the gift, a break in the day, and warmth of the a smile. All feel encouraged tha they are not forgotten in a difficult time.
                section.c-left
                    div.c-img--circle
                        img(src='img/about_relief.jpg')
                    h5 Relief Efforts
                        span Supported
                    p Many Individuals who have been through natural disasters or war have lost everything, including personal belonging and family treasures. Love Polaroids is able to help them rebuild emotionally by giving them new keepsakes.
                section.c-right
                    div.c-img--circle
                        img(src='img/about_families.jpg')
                    h5 Families
                        span Advocated
                    p Family photos have been treasured as long as they have been around. Children grow up fast, family members pass away. Life move quickly and celebrating the ones we love is important to family life.

